These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
House: farmhouse, cottage, wooden, futuristic
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, card-games, video-games, collecting
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, daisy, dahlia, zinnia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, horror, sports, animation
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 3. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growszinnia is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
 7. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 9. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
10. the person who growszinnia is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the farmhouse house##7
11. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
13. the person watching animation movies is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House   | futuristic    | cottage | wooden    | farmhouse   |
| Hobby   | cooking | video-games | card-games | collecting |
| Flower           | daisy       | dahlia   | zinnia  | orchid     |
| Movie-Genre     | zombie      | sports   | animation    | horror    |

