 4. the architect is the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
 6. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ebony##5
 7. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere between the pilot and the person who growsiris##7
 8. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5
10. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
11. the person who growsdaisy is the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
