.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, july, september, october
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, woodworking, dancing, sudoku
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, sprite, cola
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, grey, orange, white
 1. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 2. the person who likes white is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 6. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
10. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
12. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Birthday           | october | august | july | september |
| Hobby   | traveling        | sudoku    | woodworking    | dancing    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk        | cola   | soy-milk   | sprite         |
| Color           | grey          | blood-red       | white   | orange           |

