 9. the swisher-smoker is the person traveling to hannover##1
10. the turkish is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
11. the bluemaster-smoker is not the person traveling to hannover##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
