 4. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person eating watermelon##5
 6. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the old-henry-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##7
 8. the person who growsorchid is not the old-henry-smoker##6
 9. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
12. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Flower         | aconite      | amaryllis   | orchid   | sunflower       |
| Pet   | turtle | lizard    | goat | rabbit       |
| Food   | pumpkin  | lemon | watermelon   | avocado     |
| Cigar         | old-henry   | ritmeester    | vegafina   | fonseca |

