.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, rugby, snowboarding
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, november, may
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, domino, poker
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, police-officer, chef, doctor
 1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 3. the person playing poker is between the doctor and the chef##2
 4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is not the police-officer##6
 6. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
 9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person playing poker##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the person who's birthday is in november is not the chef##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
