There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, german, french, malaysian
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, white, black, red
 1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person traveling to venice and the spanish##2
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
 5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who likes white is not the french##6
 7. the french is somewhere between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to marseilles##7
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is not the person traveling to marseilles##6
 9. the malaysian is not the person traveling to prague##6
10. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who likes red##1
12. the person traveling to venice is not the owner of the rabbit##6
13. the french is on the left of the malaysian##1
14. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
15. the german is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3

