.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, coffee, juice
4 different games are played: whist, snooker, backgammon, poker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, disco, electronic, indie
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, brown, red, coral
 1. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
 2. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person who likes brown is the fan indie##1
 4. the fan electronic is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking water##2
 5. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 6. the fan techno is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person drinking fanta##7
 7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 8. the fan techno is the person who likes chestnut##1
 9. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
10. the fan disco is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
12. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice      | coffee     | water   | fanta    |
| Game     | poker | backgammon   | snooker | whist |
| Music-Genre     | indie        | electronic     | techno  | disco      |
| Color   | brown       | coral | chestnut   | red    |

 